      "para_id": "Q001847.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) For Šara , the confidant of An , the beloved child of Inana , his master , ..., the royal soldier , child of Ur-Aba , fashioned this ( bronze axe ) for the well-being of Šu-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters ."
    }
  ],
